<p>If you have any questions about the procedure, please call theÂ <a href="http://www.sickkids.ca/IGT/index.html">Image Guided Therapy (IGT) clinic</a>Â at (416) 813- 7654 ext. 201804. Speak to the IGT clinic nurse during working hours or leave a non-urgent message.</p>
